coming in on the roof.

00:09.910 --> 00:11.377
Please?

00:11.379 --> 00:12.644
For me?

00:12.646 --> 00:14.847
Damn, girl.
[ sniffs ]

00:14.849 --> 00:17.716
You know I can't say no to you
when you look at me like that.

00:17.718 --> 00:18.617
Thanks.

00:22.288 --> 00:24.857
[ mid-tempo music plays ]

00:26.793 --> 00:29.628
I saw what you did
back there.
What?

00:29.630 --> 00:32.664
The way you get people
to <i> do things</i> for you.

00:32.665 --> 00:34.733
I don't know what you're
talking about, chief.

00:34.735 --> 00:36.468
I mean, people
just do things for me

00:36.470 --> 00:37.803
Because of
my beautiful hair

00:37.805 --> 00:39.772
And my flawless skin
and my perfect melons.

00:39.774 --> 00:41.774
