with the way you pout.

00:44.478 --> 00:46.011
It's super cute.

00:46.013 --> 00:48.380
Let's try it. Ask me to do
something for you.

00:48.382 --> 00:49.615
Okay. Chief, uh,
would you be a dear

00:49.617 --> 00:50.883
And go get me
some chinese food?

00:50.885 --> 00:52.651
[ scoffs ]
go to hell, bitch!
Hey!

00:52.653 --> 00:55.254
Okay, now let's try it
with the pout.

00:55.256 --> 00:57.589
Okay.

00:57.591 --> 00:59.525
Chief,
would you be a dear?

00:59.527 --> 01:02.761
Oh, I'd do anything
for you, bitch!

01:02.763 --> 01:04.897
Gah!

01:10.070 --> 01:14.039
