billy, at school.

01:23.017 --> 01:26.251
It's blood coming out
of his penis! Now, come on!

01:26.253 --> 01:28.987
[ groans ]
oh, what to do --

01:28.989 --> 01:31.390
Go enjoy
glenn's bleeding penis,

01:31.392 --> 01:33.559
Or be a good father
to my child?

01:33.561 --> 01:35.027
You know what?

01:35.029 --> 01:37.496
I'm gonna sort this out
on my way to the break room

01:37.498 --> 01:39.164
To enjoy
glenn's bleeding penis.

01:39.166 --> 01:40.732
Yeah!

01:40.734 --> 01:42.134
Oh, there you are.
Lola.

01:42.136 --> 01:43.402
Hm.

01:43.404 --> 01:44.670
I'd like to introduce you

01:44.672 --> 01:45.771
To our new
chairman of the board.

01:45.773 --> 01:47.506
Professor
leonard hillman.

01:47.508 --> 01:49.708
Lola spratt!
My goodness.

01:49.710 --> 01:52.411
I was lola's professor
back in medical school.

01:52.413 --> 01:54.813
Oh, he was much more
than just a professor.

01:54.815 --> 01:56.882
He was a member
of the faculty

01:56.884 --> 01:59.585
At a post-graduate
learning institution.

01:59.587 --> 02:01.520
So a professor!
Yeah.

02:01.522 --> 02:02.821
