with me and billy.

03:09.723 --> 03:12.191
Oh, okay. Deal.

03:12.193 --> 03:14.526
Deal.
[ chuckles ]

03:14.528 --> 03:15.661
Here.

03:15.663 --> 03:16.929
Thank you
for the mulligan.

03:16.931 --> 03:18.263
Remember, you have
